TopicTitle: Why won't my modded part show up again?

Articles.Content:
Pic of the directory

Pic 1 of the code

Pic 2 of the code

The part wont show up at all in the game. Not in any tabs or anything, not even a gray model.
I used the KSP Addon to get rid of the Unity if that changes anything.
Any help?

You've set category to none. 

category = none

KSP does not display parts when the category is set to none. Change the category to one of the standard stock categories and it should then show up.
